---
import "../styles/main.css";
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link
			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Alegreya+Sans:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap"
			rel="stylesheet"
		/>
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Joe Murphy</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="white-on-darkblue-AAA">
			<header class="wrapper">
				<h1>Joe Murphy</h1>
				<p>
					Throughout my career, I have thrived by embedding myself
					within cross-functional teams across diverse industries,
					cultures and contexts — an adaptability that has exposed me
					to a wide range of products, organisations and human
					challenges.
				</p>
				<p>
					I bring a broad toolkit of design, facilitation and process
					techniques, combined with a deep empathy for users and an
					intuitive grasp of team dynamics and interpersonal nuance.
					Experienced in leading teams through complexity and
					ambiguity, I am valued for creating the conditions for
					genuine collaboration, meaningful alignment and impactful
					decision-making. This enables teams to reframe problems,
					transform their ways of working and evolve their products
					and services
				</p>
				<p>
					With this blend of strategic thinking, hands-on facilitation
					and organisational awareness, I am now looking to bring
					these capabilities to a team that wants to develop
					innovative products and services while genuinely evolving
					its culture and ways of working.
				</p>
				<ul class="tagpills">
					<li>Innovation</li>
					<li>Product Development</li>
					<li>Design Sprint</li>
					<li>Workshop Facilitation</li>
				</ul>
			</header>
		</div>

		<main>
			<section class="black-on-white-AAA">
				<div class="wrapper flow">
					<h2>Overview</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>
							As a design facilitator, I build and lead teams in
							creating human-centred solutions that align services
							and products with real user needs, helping
							organisations thrive. My work blends design
							thinking, strategic insight, and empathy-driven
							research to generate impactful product and service
							designs. I design a tailored process for the team
							and facilitate collaborative workshops to foster
							strategic alignment across diverse teams and deeply
							immerse myself in each project, examining the full
							user and operational experience. Through prototyping
							and testing, I ensure that solutions are innovative,
							sustainable, and ready for real-world application.
						</li>
						<li>
							I also support clients by building their internal
							design capabilities, empowering teams to innovate
							independently and create enduring change aligned
							with their mission. In addition to design,
							facilitation, and coaching, I collaborate with
							academia on design anthropology, researching
							cognitive theories related to spatial setups for
							effective collaboration.
						</li>
						<li>
							As a design facilitator, I build and guide teams to
							create human-centred solutions that align services
							and products with real user needs. My work blends
							design thinking, strategic insight and
							empathy-driven research.
						</li>
						<li>
							I strengthen internal design capabilities by
							designing bespoke processes for your team and by
							facilitating collaborative workshops across
							organisations. To create mission-aligned,
							sustainable change, I empower teams to innovate
							independently.
						</li>
						<li>
							Through collaboration with design anthropology
							academia, I study cognitive theories related to
							spatial configurations for effective collaboration.
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="white-on-green-AAA">
				<div class="wrapper flow">
					<h2>What I Do</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>
							<strong>Uncover user needs & insights</strong> – Using
							participatory research to inform design decisions.
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Facilitate co-design workshops</strong> – Helping
							teams collaborate, innovate, and develop strategies together.
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Support sustainability & well-being</strong> –
							Designing for long-term impact on people and the planet.
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="black-on-yellow-AA">
				<div class="wrapper flow">
					<h2>Services Offered</h2>
					<ul class="skill_cards">
						<li>
							<h3>Service Design</h3>
							Designing end-to-end service experiences with a focus
							on user-centered solutions that enhance customer satisfaction
							and business effectiveness.
						</li>
						<li>
							<h3>Design Research</h3>
							Conducting qualitative and quantitative research to uncover
							actionable insights about users, market needs, and service
							opportunities.
						</li>
						<li>
							<h3>Workshop Design & Facilitation</h3>
							Creating and leading interactive workshops to foster stakeholder
							engagement, team alignment, and creative problem-solving.
						</li>
						<li>
							<h3>Capability Building & Live Learning</h3>
							Embedding within teams to transfer service design skills,
							helping organizations to independently drive and sustain
							design innovation
						</li>
						<li>
							<h3>Prototyping & Testing</h3>
							Developing and iteratively testing service prototypes
							to validate ideas and refine them based on real-world
							feedback
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="darkblue-on-cyan-AA">
				<div class="wrapper flow">
					<h2>Frequent Deliverables</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>
							<strong>Customer Journey Maps</strong><br />
							Visual representations of customer experiences to identify
							pain points, opportunities, and key moments of engagement.
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Service Blueprints</strong><br />
							Comprehensive maps of service processes, detailing both
							customer-facing and behind-the-scenes interactions to
							ensure smooth, integrated service delivery.
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Personas & User Profiles</strong><br />
							Detailed profiles of key user segments, based on research,
							to guide empathetic and targeted design decisions.
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Insights Reports</strong><br />
							In-depth research summaries highlighting key user insights,
							patterns, and strategic recommendations.
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Prototypes & Mockups</strong><br />
							Interactive prototypes that showcase proposed service
							features and allow for hands-on user testing and refinement.
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Training Materials & Toolkits</strong><br />
							Custom-designed resources that empower teams to adopt
							and maintain a service design mindset and process.
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Workshop & Facilitation Reports</strong><br
							/>
							Summaries of workshop outcomes, including participant
							feedback, identified solutions, and strategic next steps.
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Design Guidelines & Documentation</strong
							><br />
							Clear guidelines and documentation to support the ongoing
							implementation and scaling of service solutions across
							the organization.
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="black-on-white-AAA">
				<div class="wrapper">
					<p>
						I believe the best solutions come from understanding
						people deeply and designing with them, not just for
						them. Let's connect and explore new ways to create
						meaningful experiences!
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
